Stargate:
API extensions: Currently there are extensions for CQL, and REST and GraphQL APIs for CRUD access to table data.
Persistence extensions: The extensions for Cassandra 3.11 and 4.0, DSE 6.8
Authentication extensions: This extension stores generated access tokens in the database.

Cass-operator: Deploys and manages Cassandra in k8ssandra. A Pod has 3 containers: api management, cassandra and config manager
Medusa: Backups and restore of cassandra cluster. Cloud storage integrations are supported
Repear: Manages repairs, schedule repairs, monitor repairs
Metrics-collector: MCAC - Metrics collector for apache cassandra. Collects cassandra & OS stats

kubebuilder:
https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kubebuilder 
